                     <interp inst="t18311020-161-person1112" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I stopped the prisoner a hundred yards from Moss door. with this parcel under his right arm - he said he had bought it; I took him back to the shop.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoenr's Defence; I picked it up, looked at it, and the Policeman collared me.</p>
